2026-05-15T05:52:40.7347913Z 55        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-05-15T05:52:40.7348701Z 56        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-05-15T05:52:40.7349584Z 57        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
2026-05-15T05:52:40.7350415Z 58        FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE notifications, preventing the
